And we're going to begin the
next class by talking about the

01:19:03.560 --> 01:19:06.685
mathematics of the prime
mortgage market and prepayments

01:19:06.685 --> 01:19:08.220
and how to value those.
 

01:19:08.220 --> 01:19:12.148
And gradually we're going to
